Graph Query languge(GraphQL)
The data will be represented in a way like Graph.


Benefits:
Avoids overfetching
Avoids underfetching
Better Mobile performance
Efficiency & Precision
Declarative data fetching
Structured/Hierarichal Structure
Strongly typed
Introspection
Real time capabilities -> subscription


